login dir: allow user to login using email and password 
data : repo : represent data to firebase 
presentation : manager : manage states loading and success and error and handle errors and handle ui 
view :ui 
 widgets : components widgets to use in view  
login or signup : ui screen show login button and signup button To choose between them

register: allow user to create her account 
data : repo : represent data to firebase and store user information to firestore database
model : represent user data to send to firebase by toJson method
presentation : manager : manage states loading and success and error and handle errors and handle ui 
view :ui 
